plăcintele, deci, Crăciun.

00:05:12.353 --> 00:05:14.564
Marcus a zis c-au jucat mult <i>Uno.</i>

00:05:14.647 --> 00:05:15.857
Zău? Chiar așa?

00:05:16.858 --> 00:05:18.443
- Ciudat.
- Ce?

00:05:19.152 --> 00:05:21.154
